ng physicians who supervise them. If you see a resident physician at your visit, the insurance claim will be submitted under the attending physician’s name. Our billing office will submit claims on your behalf regardless of your insurance. Patient Care UI Health Patient Portal Insurance Coverage Patient Privacy: HIPAA UI Health L.P. Johnson Family Health Center Insurance and Payment Policies Pregnancy Services Your Health Care Team UI Health Thyroid Disease in Pregnancy Clinic Local Affiliations About  Education  Research  Patient Care  Departments  News  Giving INFORMATION FOR: Prospective and Current Students  Faculty & Staff  Alumni & Friends  Patients  Businesses and Community RESOURCES: UIC Directory  Blackboard  Emergency Information  Contact Us  Apply Now  Give  Contact Us Connect with us!    If you have questions, comments, or problems accessing this site, please E-mail the webmaster  © Copyright 2019 University of Illinois College of Medicine   | Privacy Statement College of Medicine | Chicago | Peoria | Rockford | Urbana                                                                                                                                             